<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٨٩ ... سُورَةُ الفَجْرِ ... آياتها ٣٠ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْفَجْرِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِالوَقْتِ المَعْرُوفِ أَوَّلَ النَّهَارِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَيَالٍ عَشْرٍ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِلَيَالِي عَشْرِ ذِي الحِجَّةِ الأُوَلِ، وَمَا شَرُفَتْ بِهِ مِنْ أَعْمَالٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالشَّفْعِ وَالْوَتْرِ}</span> ... قَسَمٌ بِكُلِّ زَوْجٍ، وَفَرْدٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَسْرِ}</span> ... يَسْرِي بِظَلَامِهِ، وَجَوَابُ القَسَمِ مَحْذُوفٌ،<span class="c5"> تَقْدِيرُهُ:</span> لَتُبْعَثُنَّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِّذِي حِجْرٍ}</span> ... لِصَاحِبِ عَقْلٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِرَمَ}</span> ... قَبِيلَةِ إِرَمَ؛ نِسْبَةُ إِلَى جَدِّهِمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَاتِ الْعِمَادِ}</span> ... صَاحِبَةِ القُوَّةِ، وَالأَبْنِيَةِ المَرْفُوعَةِ عَلَى الأَعْمِدَةِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جَابُوا}</span> ... قَطَعُوا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالْوَادِ}</span> ... وَادِي القُرَى شَمَالَ غَرْبِ الجَزِيرَةِ العَرَبِيَّةِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذِي الْأَوْتَادِ}</span> ... صَاحِبِ الجُنُودِ الَّذِينَ ثَبَّتُوا مُلْكَهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طَغَوْا}</span> ... تَجَاوَزُوا الحَدَّ فِي الإِفْسَادِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَوْطَ عَذَابٍ}</span> ... عَذَابًا شَدِيدًا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَبِالْمِرْصَادِ}</span> ... يَرْقُبُ العَاصِينَ، وَيُمْهِلُهُمْ، ثُمَّ يَاخُذُهُمْ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ابْتَلَاهُ}</span> ... اخْتَبَرَهُ بِالنِّعْمَةِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَقَدَرَ}</span> ... ضَيَّقَ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>